{
  "video_id": "RplnSVTzvnU",
  "title": "How the blockchain will radically transform the economy | Bettina Warburg",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13000.0,
      "end_time": 17960.0,
      "text": "Economists have been exploring people&#39;s behavior for hundreds of years:"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18880.0,
      "end_time": 20456.0,
      "text": "how we make decisions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20480.0,
      "end_time": 23536.0,
      "text": "how we act individually and in groups,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23560.0,
      "end_time": 25279.0,
      "text": "how we exchange value."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26760.0,
      "end_time": 30216.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve studied the institutions that facilitate our trade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30240.0,
      "end_time": 31656.0,
      "text": "like legal systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31680.0,
      "end_time": 32920.0,
      "text": "corporations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33520.0,
      "end_time": 34720.0,
      "text": "marketplaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35600.0,
      "end_time": 39560.0,
      "text": "But there is a new, technological institution"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39800.0,
      "end_time": 43960.0,
      "text": "that will fundamentally change how we exchange value,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43120.0,
      "end_time": 44599.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s called the blockchain."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46400.0,
      "end_time": 48696.0,
      "text": "Now, that&#39;s a pretty bold statement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48720.0,
      "end_time": 51856.0,
      "text": "but if you take nothing else away from this talk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51880.0,
      "end_time": 53616.0,
      "text": "I actually want you to remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53640.0,
      "end_time": 57576.0,
      "text": "that while blockchain technology is relatively new,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57600.0,
      "end_time": 61976.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s also a continuation of a very human story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62000.0,
      "end_time": 63520.0,
      "text": "and the story is this."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64800.0,
      "end_time": 66960.0,
      "text": "As humans, we find ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66120.0,
      "end_time": 68936.0,
      "text": "to lower uncertainty about one another"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68960.0,
      "end_time": 70759.0,
      "text": "so that we can exchange value."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 73800.0,
      "end_time": 76575.0,
      "text": "Now, one of the first people to really explore the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 76599.0,
      "end_time": 79776.0,
      "text": "of institutions as a tool in economics"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79800.0,
      "end_time": 82256.0,
      "text": "to lower our uncertainties about one another"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82280.0,
      "end_time": 84176.0,
      "text": "and be able to do trade"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84200.0,
      "end_time": 86840.0,
      "text": "was the Nobel economist Douglass North."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87680.0,
      "end_time": 89816.0,
      "text": "He passed away at the end of 2015,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 89840.0,
      "end_time": 94560.0,
      "text": "but North pioneered what&#39;s called \"new institutional economics.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95120.0,
      "end_time": 99296.0,
      "text": "And what he meant by institutions were really just formal rules"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 99320.0,
      "end_time": 101295.0,
      "text": "like a constitution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101320.0,
      "end_time": 104240.0,
      "text": "and informal constraints, like bribery."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 105280.0,
      "end_time": 108176.0,
      "text": "These institutions are really the grease"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 108200.0,
      "end_time": 111136.0,
      "text": "that allow our economic wheels to function,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 111160.0,
      "end_time": 114280.0,
      "text": "and we can see this play out over the course of human history."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 115120.0,
      "end_time": 118576.0,
      "text": "If we think back to when we were hunter-gatherer economies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 118600.0,
      "end_time": 121536.0,
      "text": "we really just traded within our village structure."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 121560.0,
      "end_time": 123976.0,
      "text": "We had some informal constraints in place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 124000.0,
      "end_time": 127536.0,
      "text": "but we enforced all of our trade with violence"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 127560.0,
      "end_time": 129440.0,
      "text": "or social repercussions."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 129960.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132296.0,
      "text": "As our societies grew more complex"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 132320.0,
      "end_time": 135536.0,
      "text": "and our trade routes grew more distant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 135560.0,
      "end_time": 138576.0,
      "text": "we built up more formal institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 138600.0,
      "end_time": 141936.0,
      "text": "institutions like banks for currency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 141960.0,
      "end_time": 144656.0,
      "text": "governments, corporations."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 144680.0,
      "end_time": 147216.0,
      "text": "These institutions helped us manage our trade"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 147240.0,
      "end_time": 150256.0,
      "text": "as the uncertainty and the complexity grew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 150280.0,
      "end_time": 152880.0,
      "text": "and our personal control was much lower."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 153560.0,
      "end_time": 157840.0,
      "text": "Eventually with the internet, we put these same institutions online."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 158600.0,
      "end_time": 162976.0,
      "text": "We built platform marketplaces like Amazon, eBay, Alibaba,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 163000.0,
      "end_time": 166536.0,
      "text": "just faster institutions that act as middlemen"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 166560.0,
      "end_time": 169480.0,
      "text": "to facilitate human economic activity."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 171840.0,
      "end_time": 173976.0,
      "text": "As Douglass North saw it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 174000.0,
      "end_time": 177656.0,
      "text": "institutions are a tool to lower uncertainty"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 177680.0,
      "end_time": 182000.0,
      "text": "so that we can connect and exchange all kinds of value in society."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 182840.0,
      "end_time": 185176.0,
      "text": "And I believe we are now entering"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 185200.0,
      "end_time": 188176.0,
      "text": "a further and radical evolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 188200.0,
      "end_time": 190655.0,
      "text": "of how we interact and trade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 190680.0,
      "end_time": 194256.0,
      "text": "because for the first time, we can lower uncertainty"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 194280.0,
      "end_time": 197856.0,
      "text": "not just with political and economic institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 197880.0,
      "end_time": 201616.0,
      "text": "like our banks, our corporations, our governments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 201640.0,
      "end_time": 204000.0,
      "text": "but we can do it with technology alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 205920.0,
      "end_time": 207935.0,
      "text": "So what is the blockchain?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 207960.0,
      "end_time": 212160.0,
      "text": "Blockchain technology is a decentralized database"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 212400.0,
      "end_time": 215576.0,
      "text": "that stores a registry of assets and transactions"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 215600.0,
      "end_time": 217400.0,
      "text": "across a peer-to-peer network."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 218160.0,
      "end_time": 220296.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s basically a public registry"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 220320.0,
      "end_time": 223160.0,
      "text": "of who owns what and who transacts what."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 223920.0,
      "end_time": 226896.0,
      "text": "The transactions are secured through cryptography,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 226920.0,
      "end_time": 232696.0,
      "text": "and over time, that transaction history gets locked in blocks of data"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 232720.0,
      "end_time": 236200.0,
      "text": "that are then cryptographically linked together and secured."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 237360.0,
      "end_time": 241536.0,
      "text": "This creates an immutable, unforgeable record"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 241560.0,
      "end_time": 245376.0,
      "text": "of all of the transactions across this network."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 245400.0,
      "end_time": 249800.0,
      "text": "This record is replicated on every computer that uses the network."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 251240.0,
      "end_time": 252480.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not an app."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 253800.0,
      "end_time": 254320.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not a company."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 255120.0,
      "end_time": 258880.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s closest in description to something like Wikipedia."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 259800.0,
      "end_time": 261856.0,
      "text": "We can see everything on Wikipedia."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 261880.0,
      "end_time": 265920.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a composite view that&#39;s constantly changing and being updated."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 267880.0,
      "end_time": 271536.0,
      "text": "We can also track those changes over time on Wikipedia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 271560.0,
      "end_time": 273856.0,
      "text": "and we can create our own wikis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 273880.0,
      "end_time": 276719.0,
      "text": "because at their core, they&#39;re just a data infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 278600.0,
      "end_time": 284960.0,
      "text": "On Wikipedia, it&#39;s an open platform that stores words and images"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 284120.0,
      "end_time": 286600.0,
      "text": "and the changes to that data over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 287520.0,
      "end_time": 288976.0,
      "text": "On the blockchain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 289000.0,
      "end_time": 291936.0,
      "text": "you can think of it as an open infrastructure"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 291960.0,
      "end_time": 294640.0,
      "text": "that stores many kinds of assets."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 295760.0,
      "end_time": 298496.0,
      "text": "It stores the history of custodianship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 298520.0,
      "end_time": 300736.0,
      "text": "ownership and location"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 300760.0,
      "end_time": 304416.0,
      "text": "for assets like the digital currency Bitcoin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 304440.0,
      "end_time": 306160.0,
      "text": "other digital assets"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 306400.0,
      "end_time": 309360.0,
      "text": "like a title of ownership of IP."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 310480.0,
      "end_time": 313616.0,
      "text": "It could be a certificate, a contract,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 313640.0,
      "end_time": 314895.0,
      "text": "real world objects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 314920.0,
      "end_time": 317720.0,
      "text": "even personal identifiable information."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 319800.0,
      "end_time": 322936.0,
      "text": "There are of course other technical details to the blockchain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 322960.0,
      "end_time": 324976.0,
      "text": "but at its core, that&#39;s how it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 325000.0,
      "end_time": 329336.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s this public registry that stores transactions in a network"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 329360.0,
      "end_time": 333560.0,
      "text": "and is replicated so that it&#39;s very secure and hard to tamper with."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 335120.0,
      "end_time": 337256.0,
      "text": "Which brings me to my point"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 337280.0,
      "end_time": 340335.0,
      "text": "of how blockchains lower uncertainty"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 340360.0,
      "end_time": 344496.0,
      "text": "and how they therefore promise to transform our economic systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 344520.0,
      "end_time": 345719.0,
      "text": "in radical ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 347880.0,
      "end_time": 350216.0,
      "text": "So uncertainty is kind of a big term"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 350240.0,
      "end_time": 351616.0,
      "text": "in economics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 351640.0,
      "end_time": 353695.0,
      "text": "but I want to go through three forms of it"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 353720.0,
      "end_time": 357960.0,
      "text": "that we face in almost all of our everyday transactions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 357120.0,
      "end_time": 359216.0,
      "text": "where blockchains can play a role."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 359240.0,
      "end_time": 362616.0,
      "text": "We face uncertainties like not knowing who we&#39;re dealing with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 362640.0,
      "end_time": 365455.0,
      "text": "not having visibility into a transaction"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 365480.0,
      "end_time": 368400.0,
      "text": "and not having recourse if things go wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 369520.0,
      "end_time": 372880.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s take the first example, not knowing who we&#39;re dealing with."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 373720.0,
      "end_time": 377800.0,
      "text": "Say I want to buy a used smartphone on eBay."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 377760.0,
      "end_time": 381800.0,
      "text": "The first thing I&#39;m going to do is look up who I&#39;m buying from."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 381600.0,
      "end_time": 383336.0,
      "text": "Are they a power user?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 383360.0,
      "end_time": 387480.0,
      "text": "Do they have great reviews and ratings, or do they have no profile at all?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 388960.0,
      "end_time": 391736.0,
      "text": "Reviews, ratings, checkmarks:"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 391760.0,
      "end_time": 395376.0,
      "text": "these are the attestations about our identities"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 395400.0,
      "end_time": 397150.0,
      "text": "that we cobble together today"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 397400.0,
      "end_time": 400480.0,
      "text": "and use to lower uncertainty about who we&#39;re dealing with."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 401840.0,
      "end_time": 404856.0,
      "text": "But the problem is they&#39;re very fragmented."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 404880.0,
      "end_time": 407200.0,
      "text": "Think about how many profiles you have."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 408520.0,
      "end_time": 414150.0,
      "text": "Blockchains allow for us to create an open, global platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 414400.0,
      "end_time": 418416.0,
      "text": "on which to store any attestation about any individual"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 418440.0,
      "end_time": 419840.0,
      "text": "from any source."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 420480.0,
      "end_time": 423776.0,
      "text": "This allows us to create a user-controlled"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 423800.0,
      "end_time": 425160.0,
      "text": "portable identity."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 427800.0,
      "end_time": 429696.0,
      "text": "More than a profile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 429720.0,
      "end_time": 433160.0,
      "text": "it means you can selectively reveal"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 433400.0,
      "end_time": 434976.0,
      "text": "the different attributes about you"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 435000.0,
      "end_time": 438296.0,
      "text": "that help facilitate trade or interaction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 438320.0,
      "end_time": 441176.0,
      "text": "for instance that a government issued you an ID,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 441200.0,
      "end_time": 443455.0,
      "text": "or that you&#39;re over 21,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 443480.0,
      "end_time": 446960.0,
      "text": "by revealing the cryptographic proof"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 446120.0,
      "end_time": 449000.0,
      "text": "that these details exist and are signed off on."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 450960.0,
      "end_time": 453150.0,
      "text": "Having this kind of portable identity"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 453400.0,
      "end_time": 456560.0,
      "text": "around the physical world and the digital world"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 456800.0,
      "end_time": 459376.0,
      "text": "means we can do all kinds of human trade"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 459400.0,
      "end_time": 460799.0,
      "text": "in a totally new way."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 462600.0,
      "end_time": 465496.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ve talked about how blockchains could lower uncertainty"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 465520.0,
      "end_time": 467560.0,
      "text": "in who we&#39;re dealing with."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 467800.0,
      "end_time": 469656.0,
      "text": "The second uncertainty that we often face"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 469680.0,
      "end_time": 472880.0,
      "text": "is just not having transparency into our interactions."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 473600.0,
      "end_time": 476336.0,
      "text": "Say you&#39;re going to send me that smartphone by mail."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 476360.0,
      "end_time": 478560.0,
      "text": "I want some degree of transparency."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 478800.0,
      "end_time": 482376.0,
      "text": "I want to know that the product I bought is the same one that arrives in the mail"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 482400.0,
      "end_time": 484775.0,
      "text": "and that there&#39;s some record for how it got to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 484800.0,
      "end_time": 487416.0,
      "text": "This is true not just for electronics like smartphones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 487440.0,
      "end_time": 490616.0,
      "text": "but for many kinds of goods and data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 490640.0,
      "end_time": 493280.0,
      "text": "things like medicine, luxury goods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 494000.0,
      "end_time": 497520.0,
      "text": "any kind of data or product that we don&#39;t want tampered with."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 498880.0,
      "end_time": 501960.0,
      "text": "The problem in many companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 501120.0,
      "end_time": 504456.0,
      "text": "especially those that produce something complicated like a smartphone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 504480.0,
      "end_time": 506976.0,
      "text": "is they&#39;re managing all of these different vendors"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 507000.0,
      "end_time": 508880.0,
      "text": "across a horizontal supply chain."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 510240.0,
      "end_time": 512816.0,
      "text": "All of these people that go into making a product,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 512840.00000000006,
      "end_time": 514496.00000000006,
      "text": "they don&#39;t have the same database."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 514520.0,
      "end_time": 516535.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t use the same infrastructure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 516558.99999999994,
      "end_time": 521678.99999999994,
      "text": "and so it becomes really hard to see transparently a product evolve over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 523840.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525775.0,
      "text": "Using the blockchain, we can create"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 525799.0,
      "end_time": 529559.0,
      "text": "a shared reality across nontrusting entities."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 530640.0,
      "end_time": 531856.0,
      "text": "By this I mean"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 531880.0,
      "end_time": 535256.0,
      "text": "all of these nodes in the network do not need to know each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 535280.0,
      "end_time": 536696.0,
      "text": "or trust each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 536720.0,
      "end_time": 538856.0,
      "text": "because they each have the ability"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 538880.0,
      "end_time": 541960.0,
      "text": "to monitor and validate the chain for themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 543400.0,
      "end_time": 544776.0,
      "text": "Think back to Wikipedia."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 544800.0,
      "end_time": 546976.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a shared database,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 547000.0,
      "end_time": 549816.0,
      "text": "and even though it has multiple readers"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 549840.0,
      "end_time": 551936.0,
      "text": "and multiple writers at the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 551960.0,
      "end_time": 553680.0,
      "text": "it has one single truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 554720.0,
      "end_time": 556816.0,
      "text": "So we can create that using blockchains."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 556840.0,
      "end_time": 562816.0,
      "text": "We can create a decentralized database that has the same efficiency of a monopoly"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 562840.0,
      "end_time": 565520.0,
      "text": "without actually creating that central authority."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 566200.0,
      "end_time": 568616.0,
      "text": "So all of these vendors, all sorts of companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 568640.0,
      "end_time": 572600.0,
      "text": "can interact using the same database without trusting one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 574200.0,
      "end_time": 577736.0,
      "text": "It means for consumers, we can have a lot more transparency."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 577760.0,
      "end_time": 579896.0,
      "text": "As a real-world object travels along,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 579920.0,
      "end_time": 585960.0,
      "text": "we can see its digital certificate or token move on the blockchain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 585120.0,
      "end_time": 586840.0,
      "text": "adding value as it goes."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 588360.0,
      "end_time": 592200.0,
      "text": "This is a whole new world in terms of our visibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 593720.0,
      "end_time": 598320.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ve talked about how blockchains can lower our uncertainties about identity"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 599240.0,
      "end_time": 602456.0,
      "text": "and how they change what we mean about transparency"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 602480.0,
      "end_time": 606240.0,
      "text": "in long distances and complex trades, like in a supply chain."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 607520.0,
      "end_time": 609616.0,
      "text": "The last uncertainty that we often face"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 609640.0,
      "end_time": 612280.0,
      "text": "is one of the most open-ended, and it&#39;s reneging."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 612920.0,
      "end_time": 615415.0,
      "text": "What if you don&#39;t send me the smartphone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 615440.0,
      "end_time": 617000.0,
      "text": "Can I get my money back?"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 617800.0,
      "end_time": 621496.0,
      "text": "Blockchains allow us to write code,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 621520.0,
      "end_time": 623216.0,
      "text": "binding contracts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 623240.0,
      "end_time": 624896.0,
      "text": "between individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 624920.0,
      "end_time": 628575.0,
      "text": "and then guarantee that those contracts will bear out"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 628600.0,
      "end_time": 630560.0,
      "text": "without a third party enforcer."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 631720.0,
      "end_time": 635616.0,
      "text": "So if we look at the smartphone example, you could think about escrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 635640.0,
      "end_time": 637736.0,
      "text": "You are financing that phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 637760.0,
      "end_time": 640295.0,
      "text": "but you don&#39;t need to release the funds"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 640320.0,
      "end_time": 643136.0,
      "text": "until you can verify that all the conditions have been met."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 643160.0,
      "end_time": 644360.0,
      "text": "You got the phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 646240.0,
      "end_time": 648656.0,
      "text": "I think this is one of the most exciting ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 648680.0,
      "end_time": 651120.0,
      "text": "that blockchains lower our uncertainties,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 651840.0,
      "end_time": 653416.0,
      "text": "because it means to some degree"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 653440.0,
      "end_time": 657400.0,
      "text": "we can collapse institutions and their enforcement."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 659720.0,
      "end_time": 662416.0,
      "text": "It means a lot of human economic activity"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 662440.0,
      "end_time": 667456.0,
      "text": "can get collateralized and automated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 667480.0,
      "end_time": 670536.0,
      "text": "and push a lot of human intervention to the edges,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 670560.0,
      "end_time": 674520.0,
      "text": "the places where information moves from the real world to the blockchain."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 676880.0,
      "end_time": 679336.0,
      "text": "I think what would probably floor Douglass North"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 679360.0,
      "end_time": 681736.0,
      "text": "about this use of technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 681760.0,
      "end_time": 684776.0,
      "text": "is the fact that the very thing that makes it work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 684800.0,
      "end_time": 689335.0,
      "text": "the very thing that keeps the blockchain secure and verified,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 689360.0,
      "end_time": 691320.0,
      "text": "is our mutual distrust."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 693600.0,
      "end_time": 696696.0,
      "text": "So rather than all of our uncertainties"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 696720.0,
      "end_time": 698336.0,
      "text": "slowing us down"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 698360.0,
      "end_time": 700856.0,
      "text": "and requiring institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 700880.0,
      "end_time": 703960.0,
      "text": "like banks, our governments, our corporations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 705360.0,
      "end_time": 709736.0,
      "text": "we can actually harness all of that collective uncertainty"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 709760.0,
      "end_time": 715360.0,
      "text": "and use it to collaborate and exchange more and faster and more open."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 716800.0,
      "end_time": 718856.0,
      "text": "Now, I don&#39;t want you to get the impression"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 718880.0,
      "end_time": 721256.0,
      "text": "that the blockchain is the solution to everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 721280.0,
      "end_time": 726199.0,
      "text": "even though the media has said that it&#39;s going to end world poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 727840.0,
      "end_time": 730576.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s also going to solve the counterfeit drug problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 730600.0,
      "end_time": 732800.0,
      "text": "and potentially save the rainforest."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 734320.0,
      "end_time": 738296.0,
      "text": "The truth is, this technology is in its infancy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 738320.0,
      "end_time": 741536.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re going to need to see a lot of experiments take place"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 741560.0,
      "end_time": 742976.0,
      "text": "and probably fail"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 743000.0,
      "end_time": 746536.0,
      "text": "before we truly understand all of the use cases"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 746560.0,
      "end_time": 747760.0,
      "text": "for our economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 749240.0,
      "end_time": 751416.0,
      "text": "But there are tons of people working on this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 751440.0,
      "end_time": 753136.0,
      "text": "from financial institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 753160.0,
      "end_time": 756319.0,
      "text": "to technology companies, start-ups and universities."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 757120.0,
      "end_time": 762560.0,
      "text": "And one of the reasons is that it&#39;s not just an economic evolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 762800.0,
      "end_time": 765800.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also an innovation in computer science."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 769360.0,
      "end_time": 772816.0,
      "text": "Blockchains give us the technological capability"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 772840.0,
      "end_time": 776416.0,
      "text": "of creating a record of human exchange,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 776440.0,
      "end_time": 778000.0,
      "text": "of exchange of currency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 778720.0,
      "end_time": 782416.0,
      "text": "of all kinds of digital and physical assets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 782440.0,
      "end_time": 785160.0,
      "text": "even of our own personal attributes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 785400.0,
      "end_time": 786360.0,
      "text": "in a totally new way."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 787720.0,
      "end_time": 789560.0,
      "text": "So in some ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 789800.0,
      "end_time": 792560.0,
      "text": "they become a technological institution"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 792800.0,
      "end_time": 793856.0,
      "text": "that has a lot of the benefits"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 793880.0,
      "end_time": 797800.0,
      "text": "of the traditional institutions we&#39;re used to using in society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 798200.0,
      "end_time": 801120.0,
      "text": "but it does this in a decentralized way."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 802360.0,
      "end_time": 805896.0,
      "text": "It does this by converting a lot of our uncertainties"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 805920.0,
      "end_time": 807120.0,
      "text": "into certainties."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 808360.0,
      "end_time": 811896.0,
      "text": "So I think we need to start preparing ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 811920.0,
      "end_time": 814455.0,
      "text": "because we are about to face a world"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 814480.0,
      "end_time": 817616.0,
      "text": "where distributed, autonomous institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 817640.0,
      "end_time": 819640.0,
      "text": "have quite a significant role."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 820600.0,
      "end_time": 821816.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 821840.0,
      "end_time": 824200.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 830400.0,
      "end_time": 832670.0,
      "text": "Bruno Giussani: Thank you, Bettina."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 832880.0,
      "end_time": 836576.0,
      "text": "I think I understood that it&#39;s coming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 836600.0,
      "end_time": 838496.0,
      "text": "it offers a lot of potential,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 838520.0,
      "end_time": 840696.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s complex."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 840720.0,
      "end_time": 845800.0,
      "text": "What is your estimate for the rate of adoption?"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 847120.0,
      "end_time": 849736.0,
      "text": "Bettina Warburg: I think that&#39;s a really good question."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 849760.0,
      "end_time": 851176.0,
      "text": "My lab is pretty much focused"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 851200.0,
      "end_time": 854656.0,
      "text": "on going the enterprise and government route first,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 854680.0,
      "end_time": 858215.0,
      "text": "because in reality, blockchain is a complex technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 858240.0,
      "end_time": 861160.0,
      "text": "How many of you actually understand how the internet works?"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 861400.0,
      "end_time": 862695.0,
      "text": "But you use it every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 862720.0,
      "end_time": 866496.0,
      "text": "so I think we&#39;re sort of facing the same John Sculley idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 866520.0,
      "end_time": 870175.0,
      "text": "of technology should either be invisible or beautiful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 870200.0,
      "end_time": 874560.0,
      "text": "and blockchain is kind of neither of those things right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 874800.0,
      "end_time": 878560.0,
      "text": "so it&#39;s better suited for either really early adopters"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 878800.0,
      "end_time": 880296.0,
      "text": "who kind of get it and can tinker around"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 880320.0,
      "end_time": 883296.0,
      "text": "or for finding those best use cases"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 883320.0,
      "end_time": 886496.0,
      "text": "like identity or asset tracking or smart contracts"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 886520.0,
      "end_time": 890536.0,
      "text": "that can be used at that level of an enterprise or government."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 890560.0,
      "end_time": 892464.0,
      "text": "BG: Thank you. Thanks for coming to TED."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 892489.0,
      "end_time": 893696.0,
      "text": "BW: Thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 893720.0,
      "end_time": 896120.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}